name: Genius: Into the Toy Warehouses
overview: Genius: Into the Toy Warehouses is a 2016 homebrew platform puzzler written by Daniele Liverani. The goal is to obtain all the keys in order to open the main door which also contains an items) you must collect. Be careful as some of the rooms have monsters and bombs inside them. Getting to a detonator at least takes care of the bombs.
